hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但無依種氣魄<br />\n我地一個經濟圈未成氣候、未統一戰線已經自己搞死自己，更點講未來組織影子內閣、組織政府"},{"pid":"784f1e397e4e15b2b474a687400d3df63db2b857","tid":1958824,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5352f45764a2e205955bab892d50cf6722b4260f","tid":1958824,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T00:41:20.000Z","msg":"黃子華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:16:25.000Z","msg":"大把人衝入戲院睇戲話撐黃色經濟圈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n子華未出聲因為要顧及套戲既票房，套戲落畫就會出聲了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22413c539be2ffce43c46db001d2780a89619a2e","tid":1958824,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:21:01.000Z","msg":"唔知由幾時開始就無視咗政治中立嘅個立場"},{"pid":"dd3294e468fe494e1ee24b0bfbd88b0ae9099a5b","tid":1958824,"uid":230239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22413c539be2ffce43c46db001d2780a89619a2e","tid":1958824,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:21:01.000Z","msg":"唔知由幾時開始就無視咗政治中立嘅個立場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:49:41.000Z","msg":"連登仔唔係話中立衰過藍絲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c4e27cf0bf9f85c557fc7b55452ecdd4a6df23","tid":1958824,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T07:35:33.000Z","msg":"大集團好難黃出面，香港做得大生意，肯定同中國有來往，啲高層有錢佬一樣，睇住中共面色做人"}]}